name: TrailCurrent Libraries
description: Symbols, footprints, and 3D models for the TrailCurrent open-source vehicle platform.
description_full:
Consolidated KiCAD library package for the TrailCurrent open-source vehicle platform.

Includes custom symbols, footprints, and 3D models for:
- CAN bus components (MCP2515, SN65HVD230DR)
- DC-DC converters (AP63203WU-7)
- Crystals and passives
- JST XH connector series
- Custom connectors

For more information, visit https://trailcurrent.com
